&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Associação Software Livre.Org&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 02 Jul 2017 14:42:49 +0000</pubDate><link>http://softwarelivre.org/asl/noticias/inscricoes-abertas-para-o-fisl18</link><guid>http://softwarelivre.org/asl/noticias/inscricoes-abertas-para-o-fisl18</guid></item><item><title>Adiamento Assembleia Geral Ordinária</title><description>&lt;p&gt;A Coordenação Geral da Associação Software Livre.Org comunica que a Assembleia Geral Ordinária, convocada anteriormente para o dia 23/11/2016,  foi adiada para o dia  14/12/2016 conforme informado aos associados na semana passada.   Segue novo edital de convocação:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5 class="western" align="center"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: FreeSans,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;EDITAL DE CONVOCAÇÃO &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;" align="center"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5 class="western" align="center"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: FreeSans,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;N&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;° 001/201&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6 – A&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SSEMBLEIA GERAL &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ORDINÁRIA&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;" align="center"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0cm;" align="justify"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;" align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: FreeSans,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;O Coordenador Ge&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;ral &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;da &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Associação Software Livre.Org&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;, no uso das atribuições que lhe confere o Estatuto Social, convoca todos os associados da entidade para reunirem-se em Assembleia Ger&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;al Ordinária,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; a realizar-se no dia &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;14 de dezembro&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; de 2016&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;no TECNOPUC – Parque Tecnológico da PUCRS, na Sala 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;04&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; do Prédio 99A&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;, localizad&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;na Av. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Ipiranga, 6681&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; em Porto Alegre – RS, às &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;18h&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;, em primeira chamada, com a presença de 2/3 (dois terços) dos associados e às &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;19h&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;em &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;segunda &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;e última chamada com qualquer quorum, para deliberarem sobre a seguinte ordem do dia:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;" align="justify"&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 150%;" align="justify"&gt;&lt;span style="font-family: FreeSans,sans-serif;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: small;"&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Leitura da Ata da Assembleia anterior;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
